msgctxt "2768"
msgid "Batting Abilities"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44_Batting Abilities"
msgid ""
"\r\n"
"In Shinada's Side Story \"The Cost of a Swing,\"  Shinada's batting skills "
"can be improved to give an advantage when taking on challengers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56_Batting Abilities"
msgid ""
"\r\n"
"Shinada's batting skills are improved by playing various courses at the "
"batting center."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68_Batting Abilities"
msgid ""
"\r\n"
"The bat's swing has four impact ranges that are assigned to four buttons: "
"<Action:Button_Circle@Cost_Of_A_Swing>, "
"<Action:Button_Triangle@Cost_Of_A_Swing>, "
"<Action:Button_Square@Cost_Of_A_Swing> "
"and<Action:Button_Cross@Cost_Of_A_Swing>. If an impact range levels up, its "
"Swing Cursor is enlarged, making it easier to hit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80_Batting Abilities"
msgid ""
"\r\n"
"If the impact timing levels up, the window of opportunity for hitting a "
"home run is extended."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92_Batting Abilities"
msgid ""
"\r\n"
"If the fouling skill levels up, the window of opportunity for fouling off "
"pitches is extended.\r\n"
"This is useful in situations where Shinada needs to cut pitches."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104_Batting Abilities"
msgid ""
"\r\n"
"If Heat Eye levels up, pitches will appear even slower when using the Heat "
"Eye ability."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116_Batting Abilities"
msgid ""
"\r\n"
"If Batting Eye levels up, the pink circle that indicates the ball's "
"anticipated trajectory becomes smaller, making it easier to hit. It also "
"improves the precision of the anticipated pitch indicator at the screen's "
"bottom right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128_Batting Abilities"
msgid ""
"\r\n"
"These skills can be leveled up by playing the various courses at the "
"batting center, and by progressing through Shinada's Side Story. View "
"current skill levels by speaking to the clerk at the batting center."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140_Batting Abilities"
msgid ""
"\r\n"
"As he progresses through the Side Story, Shinada will face old rivals as "
"well as new challengers.\r\n"
"Facing them will also hone Shinada's batting skills."
msgstr ""